function handler(document)
    -- Write a log message
    log_info("Processing a document")
 
    -- Perform modifications to the document
    document:addField("some_field", "some_field_value")

    if document:hasField("NZTOWNS") then
        return document
    end
end

labels.label:
Template Showing an example of mixing Eduction and 
ExecuteLua processors 
Using the Eduction processor and add Metadata to certain files
The lua processor then splits the files dependent on whether the
metadata is added.

To use, simply use the get processor to get the wanted files, add the
correct grammar file to the Eduction processor with the correct
entity/entity fields.
Then adjust the Lua script based on your eduction processor.
